thread.title: Jacqueline Wolfe
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Jacqueline Wolfe

author: Jacqueline Wolfe
title: Jacqueline Wolfe
text: Very nice!! You have wonderful communication and updates on the delivery. The packaging was perfect and my little friends arrived alive and healthy. Perfect for a dip in the pot. I prefer cold lobster, naked. No butter. Tasted just like the Atlantic Ocean, just as I expected.
